Sentencas: Alternating current complex impedance spectroscopy studies were conducted on symmetrical cells of the type [gas, electrode/La1-xSrxGa1-yMgyO3 (LSGM) electrolyte/electrode, gas].
Titulo: Polarization study on doped lanthanum gallate electrolyte using impedance spectroscopy

Sentencas: The electrode materials were slurry-coated on both sides of the LSGM electrolyte support.
Titulo: Polarization study on doped lanthanum gallate electrolyte using impedance spectroscopy

Sentencas: The electrodes selected for this investigation are candidate materials for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) electrodes.
Titulo: Polarization study on doped lanthanum gallate electrolyte using impedance spectroscopy

Sentencas: Cathode materials include La1-xSrxMnO3 (LSM), La1-xSrxCoyFe1-yO3 (LSCF), a two-phase particulate composite consisting of LSM and doped-lanthanum gallate (LSGM), and LSCF + LSGM.
Titulo: Polarization study on doped lanthanum gallate electrolyte using impedance spectroscopy

Sentencas: Pt metal electrodes were also used for the purpose of comparison.
Titulo: Polarization study on doped lanthanum gallate electrolyte using impedance spectroscopy

Sentencas: Anode material investigated was the Ni + Ce0.85Gd0.15O2 composite.
Titulo: Polarization study on doped lanthanum gallate electrolyte using impedance spectroscopy

Sentencas: The study revealed important details pertaining.
Titulo: Polarization study on doped lanthanum gallate electrolyte using impedance spectroscopy

Sentencas: to the charge-transfer reactions that occur in such electrodes.
Titulo: Polarization study on doped lanthanum gallate electrolyte using impedance spectroscopy

Sentencas: The information obtained can be used to design electrodes for intermediate temperature SOFCs based on LSGM electrolytes.
Titulo: Polarization study on doped lanthanum gallate electrolyte using impedance spectroscopy
